text:
Weather is no longer displayed on the Calendar in Outlook - Microsoft Support
 Images are blocked and meeting body is read only in Outlook Desktop if calendar items are from other senders for Microsoft Outlook Spoofing Vulnerability released August 8, 2023 - Microsoft Support
 Outlook blocks opening FQDN and IP address hyperlinks after installing protections for Microsoft Outlook Security Feature Bypass Vulnerability released July 11, 2023 - Microsoft Support
 -- %40CH2PR01MB5640.prod.exchangelabs.com
